{
  "_comment": [
    "NOTE: Classifying consumables and traps as 'filler' because:",
    "1. If consumables/life caps are 'useful', then they will be prioritized",
    "   over filler/traps when filling extra checks, preventing traps",
    "   from generating in the item pool (since there are more consumables",
    "   + life caps than extra checks).",
    "2. The 'filler_traps' slider in the Options Creator only overwrites",
    "   generic filler, so will never overwrite the consumables/life caps",
    "   specified here. Hacky workaround is to make the traps filler",
    "   so they are drawn from the same item pool as consumables/life caps."
